  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to lsof</title>

    <para>
      The <application>lsof</application> package is useful to LiSt Open
      Files for a given running application or process.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
